init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So of course, when he disappeared this time, the entire world searched for him again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After three months of searching, not a single lead was found.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The anomaly was very interesting in that it appeared to be traveling at a speed that would take it all the way into outer space.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "So why would they kidnap Matt Damon?" asked the president.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We have to think of a plan," said the president, "but why do they need to be entertained?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Maybe we could ask the aliens to make a list of their favorite Earth entertainers," said the president.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Everyone agreed that this was a good idea and we started on our list of possible entertainers.
